---
title: One-Pot Shrimp & Bean Soup with Kale & Carrot
description: The best kind of soup? One made in a single pot that cooks up delicious flavor in just 20 minutes. This one does just that. Meaty Italian chicken sausage, kale, and carrot are simmered together in a rich, gently creamy chicken stock, and then cannellini beans are stirred in for even more hearty flavor. Even though it's super-satisfying, you won't be able to resist another spoonful.
